comments.raw_text:
+++ This bug was initially created as a clone of Bug #608152 +++

There have been some changes and an additional dialog introduced by bug 607295 related to message archiving which will become effective in SeaMonkey 2.2+:

 - New group "Message Archives" which is moving up the "Archives" selection;
 - a new checkbox to enable or disable the archiving feature for this account;
 - a new button "Archive Options" to open up a new dialog window:
   - allows to select the archiving granularity (flat, month, year)
   - allows to mirror original folder structure in the Archives folder;
   - an example tree demonstrates the effect of either option;
   - the "Archive Options" button is not available for Gmail accounts
     (bug 640342 and dependent bugs).

These changes require updates in mailnews_account_settings.xhtml, lines 443+.

